---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Neo Brutalism
description: Bold, raw design with stark contrasts, geometric shapes, and unapologetic visual weight. Digital brutalism for the modern web.
---

<section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div
    style="
      max-width: 1440px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding-left: var(--swiss-grid-margin);
      padding-right: var(--swiss-grid-margin);
    "
  >
    {# Header #}
    <div
      class="swiss-grid mb-16"
      style="
        border-left: 6px solid #ff0000;
        padding-left: var(--space-md);
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffff00 0%, #ffff00 2px, transparent 2px);
      "
    >
      <div class="swiss-col-8">
        <p
          class="font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2"
          style="color: #000000; font-size: 0.8rem; transform: rotate(-1deg); display: inline-block"
        >
          ⚡ DESIGN REBELLION
        </p>
        <h1
          class="font-bold mb-4"
          style="
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem);
            line-height: 0.9;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            color: #000000;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #ff0000;
            transform: rotate(-0.5deg);
          "
        >
          {{ title }}
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-lg mb-4"
          style="
            color: #333333;
            max-width: 55ch;
            line-height: 1.4;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #ffff00;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border: 2px solid #000000;
            box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #ff0000;
          "
        >
          {{ description }}
        </p>
        <p
          style="
            color: #666666;
            max-width: 60ch;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-left: 4px solid #000000;
            padding-left: 1rem;
          "
        >
          Aggressive, confrontational design that breaks conventional rules and demands attention through raw visual
          power.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    {# Color Palette #}
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="font-bold mb-6" style="font-size: var(--fluid-h3); color: #000000; text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #ff0000">
        Color Arsenal
      </h2>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem">
        <div
          style="
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 3px solid #000000;
            transform: rotate(1deg);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 #ff0000;
          "
        >
          <div style="height: 120px; background: #000000; border: 2px solid #ffffff; margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0; color: #000000; text-transform: uppercase">PURE BLACK</h3>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; color: #666666; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600">DOMINANCE</p>
          <code
            style="font-size: 0.75rem; background: #ffff00; padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; color: #000000; font-weight: bold"
            >#000000</code
          >
        </div>
        <div
          style="
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 3px solid #000000;
            transform: rotate(-1deg);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 #ff0000;
          "
        >
          <div style="height: 120px; background: #ff0000; border: 2px solid #000000; margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0; color: #000000; text-transform: uppercase">DANGER RED</h3>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; color: #666666; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600">AGGRESSION</p>
          <code
            style="font-size: 0.75rem; background: #ffff00; padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; color: #000000; font-weight: bold"
            >#ff0000</code
          >
        </div>
        <div
          style="
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 3px solid #000000;
            transform: rotate(0.5deg);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 #ff0000;
          "
        >
          <div style="height: 120px; background: #ffff00; border: 2px solid #000000; margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0; color: #000000; text-transform: uppercase">
            SHOCK YELLOW
          </h3>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; color: #666666; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600">ATTENTION</p>
          <code
            style="font-size: 0.75rem; background: #ffff00; padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; color: #000000; font-weight: bold"
            >#ffff00</code
          >
        </div>
        <div
          style="
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 3px solid #000000;
            transform: rotate(-0.5deg);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 #ff0000;
          "
        >
          <div style="height: 120px; background: #ffffff; border: 3px solid #000000; margin-bottom: 1rem"></div>
          <h3 style="font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0; color: #000000; text-transform: uppercase">
            STARK WHITE
          </h3>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; color: #666666; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600">CONTRAST</p>
          <code
            style="font-size: 0.75rem; background: #ffff00; padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; color: #000000; font-weight: bold"
            >#ffffff</code
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# Typography #}
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="font-bold mb-6" style="font-size: var(--fluid-h3); color: #000000; text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #ff0000">
        Typography Warfare
      </h2>
      <div style="background: #ffffff; border: 4px solid #000000; padding: 3rem; box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 #ff0000">
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div style="background: #ffff00; border: 2px solid #000000; padding: 1.5rem; transform: rotate(-0.5deg)">
            <h1
              style="
                font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
                margin: 0;
                line-height: 0.8;
                letter-spacing: -0.03em;
                font-weight: 900;
                color: #000000;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #ff0000;
              "
            >
              BRUTAL IMPACT
            </h1>
            <p
              style="color: #666666; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase"
            >
              MAXIMUM WEIGHT — ZERO SUBTLETY
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="border-left: 6px solid #ff0000; padding-left: 1.5rem">
            <h2
              style="
                font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
                margin: 0;
                font-weight: 800;
                color: #000000;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 0.02em;
              "
            >
              SECONDARY ASSAULT
            </h2>
            <p
              style="
                color: #666666;
                margin-top: 0.75rem;
                font-size: 0.875rem;
                font-weight: 600;
                text-transform: uppercase;
              "
            >
              BOLD AND UNCOMPROMISING
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="background: #000000; color: #ffffff; padding: 1.5rem; border: 2px solid #ff0000">
            <p
              style="
                margin: 0;
                font-size: 1.125rem;
                line-height: 1.3;
                font-weight: 600;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 0.01em;
              "
            >
              BODY TEXT THAT REFUSES TO BE IGNORED. EVERY WORD CARRIES WEIGHT AND PURPOSE. NO ROOM FOR WEAKNESS.
            </p>
            <p style="color: #ffff00; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700">
              AGGRESSIVE READABILITY
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="border: 2px dashed #000000; padding: 1rem">
            <p
              style="
                color: #666666;
                margin: 0;
                font-size: 0.875rem;
                line-height: 1.4;
                font-weight: 500;
                text-transform: uppercase;
              "
            >
              SUPPORTING TEXT MAINTAINS THE BRUTAL AESTHETIC WHILE PROVIDING NECESSARY INFORMATION WITHOUT COMPROMISE.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# Components #}
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="font-bold mb-6" style="font-size: var(--fluid-h3); color: #000000; text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #ff0000">
        Combat Interface
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        {# Buttons #}
        <div
          style="
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 4px solid #000000;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 #ff0000;
            transform: rotate(0.5deg);
          "
        >
          <h3
            style="font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 2rem 0; color: #000000; font-size: 1.125rem; text-transform: uppercase"
          >
            BUTTON ARSENAL
          </h3>
          <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 2rem; align-items: center">
            <button
              style="
                background: #ff0000;
                color: #ffffff;
                border: 3px solid #000000;
                padding: 1rem 2rem;
                font-weight: 800;
                font-size: 1rem;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                cursor: pointer;
                box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #000000;
                transition: all 0.1s;
                transform: rotate(-1deg);
              "
            >
              DESTROY
            </button>
            <button
              style="
                background: #ffff00;
                color: #000000;
                border: 3px solid #000000;
                padding: 1rem 2rem;
                font-weight: 800;
                font-size: 1rem;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                cursor: pointer;
                box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #000000;
                transition: all 0.1s;
                transform: rotate(1deg);
              "
            >
              ATTACK
            </button>
            <button
              style="
                background: #000000;
                color: #ffffff;
                border: 3px solid #ffffff;
                padding: 1rem 2rem;
                font-weight: 800;
                font-size: 1rem;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                cursor: pointer;
                box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #ff0000;
                transition: all 0.1s;
              "
            >
              ANNIHILATE
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        {# Form Elements #}
        <div
          style="
            background: #ffff00;
            border: 4px solid #000000;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 #ff0000;
            transform: rotate(-0.3deg);
          "
        >
          <h3
            style="font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 2rem 0; color: #000000; font-size: 1.125rem; text-transform: uppercase"
          >
            DATA CAPTURE
          </h3>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem">
            <div>
              <label
                style="
                  display: block;
                  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
                  font-weight: 800;
                  color: #000000;
                  font-size: 0.9rem;
                  text-transform: uppercase;
                "
                >EMAIL WARFARE</label
              >
              <input
                type="email"
                placeholder="YOUR.EMAIL@BATTLEFIELD.COM"
                style="
                  width: 100%;
                  padding: 1rem;
                  border: 3px solid #000000;
                  font-size: 0.95rem;
                  font-weight: 600;
                  background: #ffffff;
                  text-transform: uppercase;
                  box-shadow: inset 2px 2px 0 #ff0000;
                "
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label
                style="
                  display: block;
                  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
                  font-weight: 800;
                  color: #000000;
                  font-size: 0.9rem;
                  text-transform: uppercase;
                "
                >TERRITORY</label
              >
              <select
                style="
                  width: 100%;
                  padding: 1rem;
                  border: 3px solid #000000;
                  font-size: 0.95rem;
                  font-weight: 600;
                  background: #ffffff;
                  text-transform: uppercase;
                  box-shadow: inset 2px 2px 0 #ff0000;
                "
              >
                <option>CHOOSE YOUR DOMAIN</option>
                <option>DIGITAL WASTELAND</option>
                <option>CODE BATTLEFIELD</option>
                <option>DESIGN WARZONE</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# Cards #}
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="font-bold mb-6" style="font-size: var(--fluid-h3); color: #000000; text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #ff0000">
        Content Blocks
      </h2>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem">
        <article
          style="
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 4px solid #000000;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 #ff0000;
            transform: rotate(1deg);
          "
        >
          <h3
            style="
              font-weight: 800;
              margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
              color: #000000;
              font-size: 1.25rem;
              text-transform: uppercase;
              letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            "
          >
            BRUTAL TRUTH
          </h3>
          <p style="margin: 0; color: #333333; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase">
            CONTENT THAT CONFRONTS AND CHALLENGES. NO SUGAR-COATING. NO COMPROMISE.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article
          style="
            background: #ffff00;
            border: 4px solid #000000;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 #ff0000;
            transform: rotate(-1deg);
          "
        >
          <h3
            style="
              font-weight: 800;
              margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
              color: #000000;
              font-size: 1.25rem;
              text-transform: uppercase;
              letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            "
          >
            DIRECT ACTION
          </h3>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 2rem 0; color: #333333; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase">
            EVERY INTERACTION DEMANDS ATTENTION. EVERY CLICK IS A STATEMENT.
          </p>
          <button
            style="
              background: #ff0000;
              color: #ffffff;
              border: 2px solid #000000;
              padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
              font-weight: 800;
              font-size: 0.9rem;
              text-transform: uppercase;
              cursor: pointer;
              box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #000000;
            "
          >
            ENGAGE
          </button>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# Design Principles #}
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-bold mb-8" style="font-size: var(--fluid-h3); color: #000000; text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #ff0000">
        Combat Doctrine
      </h2>
      <div style="background: #000000; border: 4px solid #ff0000; padding: 3rem; color: #ffffff">
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 3rem">
          <div style="border-left: 4px solid #ffff00; padding-left: 1.5rem">
            <h3 style="font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; color: #ffff00; text-transform: uppercase">
              MAXIMUM CONTRAST
            </h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase">
              NO SUBTLE GRADIENTS. BLACK AND WHITE. RED AND YELLOW. PURE OPPOSITION.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="border-left: 4px solid #ffff00; padding-left: 1.5rem">
            <h3 style="font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; color: #ffff00; text-transform: uppercase">
              GEOMETRIC AGGRESSION
            </h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase">
              SHARP EDGES. BOLD SHAPES. NO SOFT CURVES OR GENTLE TRANSITIONS.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="border-left: 4px solid #ffff00; padding-left: 1.5rem">
            <h3 style="font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; color: #ffff00; text-transform: uppercase">
              FUNCTIONAL BRUTALITY
            </h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase">
              FORM FOLLOWS FUNCTION, BUT FUNCTION IS AGGRESSIVE AND UNCOMPROMISING.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div style="border-left: 4px solid #ffff00; padding-left: 1.5rem">
            <h3 style="font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; color: #ffff00; text-transform: uppercase">
              DIGITAL REBELLION
            </h3>
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase">
              BREAK CONVENTIONS. REJECT SMOOTH. EMBRACE THE HARSH BEAUTY OF RAW DIGITAL POWER.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>
